    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>Tutanota is the world's most secure email service, easy to use and private by design. Sign up for free encrypted email now.

With end-to-end encryption and 2FA, your emails have never been more secure. The built-in encryption guarantees that your mailbox belongs to you: Nobody can decrypt or read your data.

**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.</description>
    <summary>Tutanota is an email client with a strong focus on security and privacy that lets you encrypt emails on all your devices.</summary>
    <releaseNotes># What's new
- Change mark unread behavior to only mark the latest mail in the current list when list is set to group by conversation [#9545](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/9545)
- Add "Reapply inbox rules" action to `Settings &gt; Email &gt; Inbox rules` [#10461](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10461)
- Enforcing password change should apply to new users [#10458](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10458)
- Allow navigating to `Settings &gt; Email &gt; Undo send` using Quick Actions [#10492](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10492)
- Improvements to similar contact name comparison [#10497](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10497)
- Ignore extra whitespace when comparing contacts for merging [#10497](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10497)
- Too much empty space in the MailViewerHeader when the sender name isn't set [#9547](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/9547)
- Always pass id encoding when comparing ids of entities [#10746](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10746)
- Update Request Size Limit Map [#10523](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10523)
- Update Electron to v42.0.0

# Bugfixes
- Incorrect counters caused by counter fixup while client is still syncing [#10761](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10761)
- Index quick extend action does nothing on Free Accounts [#10700](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10700)
- Search URL is not updated when viewing different mails in the list [#10674](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10674)
- Cannot set offline range date more than 20 years from settings [#10673](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10673)
- Uncaught Illegal key length error when entering incorrect Recovery Key [#10602](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10602)
- Inbox rule priority not respected when "Never send it to spam" is unchecked [#10598](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10598)
- Drafted email will not delete [#10522](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10522)
- No contact found when viewing a contact list entry if the contact's email address has uppercase characters [#10499](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10499)
- Invalid SpellCheckerDictionaryDownloadURL when updateUrl isn't set [#10490](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10490)
- Spellchecker doesn't work on first launch until spellcheck language is changed [#10487](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10487)
- ProgrammingError when loading mailDetailsBlob immediately after sending a draft [#10476](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10476)
- Be able to properly undo deleted inline image [#10468](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10468)
- Check for email count text is not correct [#10467](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10467)
- [windows] EPERM, Permission denied error when setting Default mail handler [#10435](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10435)
- Mac client update fails when the client is ran from a read-only volume [#10185](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10185)
- Unset repository url error during custom desktop release [#10465](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10465)

